ou will follow later.&rdquo; 37 Peter *said to Him, &ldquo;Lord, why can I not follow You right now? I will lay down my life for You.&rdquo; 38 Jesus *answered, &ldquo;Will you lay down your life for Me? Truly, truly, I say to you, a rooster will not crow until you deny Me three times.
