at are the two olive branches which are beside the two golden pipes, which empty the golden oil from themselves?&rdquo; So he answered me, saying, &ldquo;Do you not know what these are?&rdquo; And I said, &ldquo;No, my lord.&rdquo; Then he said, &ldquo;These are the two anointed ones who are standing by the Lord of the whole earth.&rdquo;
